Harissa
  --Cook's Illustrated

6 tbsp evoo
6 garlic cloves
2 tbsp paprika
1 tbsp ground coriander
1 tbsp ground dried aleppo pepper
1 tsp ground cumin
3/4 tsp caraway seeds
1/2 tso salt

Combine all ingredients in bowl and microwave until bubbling and very fragrant, ~1 min, stirring halfway through; let cool completely. Can be refrigerated for up to 4 days.


Note: If you can't find aleppo pepper, sub 3/4 tsp paprika and 3/4 tsp finely chopped red pepper flakes.
